{"type":"message","id":"ab5f0978","parentId":"3e8388c9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T07:50:26.013Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-02-27 15:50 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【安装UIAutomation模块并验证三个方案】\n\n任务：在Windows上安装UIAutomation模块，并验证三个方案是否可以解决UI定位问题。\n\n**当前环境信息：**\n- Windows用户名: yuyirong\n- PowerShell路径: /mnt/c/Windows/System32/windowspowershell/v1.0/powershell.exe\n- 当前运行中的进程PID: 19944 (有窗口标题\"新版小豆芽\")\n\n**安装步骤：**\n\n1. **安装UIAutomation模块**\n   ```powershell\n   Install-Module -Name UIAutomation -Scope CurrentUser -Force\n   ```\n\n2. **验证安装成功**\n   ```powershell\n   Import-Module UIAutomation\n   Get-Command -Module UIAutomation | Select-Object -First 10\n   ```\n\n3. **测试UI定位功能**\n   ```powershell\n   $window = Get-UiaWindow -Name \"新版小豆芽\"\n   $window | Get-UiaButton | Select-Object -First 5\n   ```\n\n4. **尝试找到\"小红书\"入口**\n   ```powershell\n   # 列出所有按钮\n   $buttons = $window | Get-UiaButton\n   $buttons | ForEach-Object { $_.Current.Name }\n   \n   # 查找包含\"小红书\"的按钮\n   $xhsButton = $buttons | Where-Object { $_.Current.Name -like \"*小红书*\" }\n   if ($xhsButton) {\n       $xhsButton | Invoke-UiaButtonClick\n   }\n   ```\n\n5. **尝试发布帖子**\n   - 找到\"发布\"或\"发送\"按钮\n   - 使用UIAutomation点击\n\n**输出要求：**\n1. 安装过程的完整输出\n2. UIAutomation模块验证结果\n3. 小豆芽窗口的UI控件列表\n4. 是否找到\"小红书\"入口\n5. 是否成功点击发布按钮\n6. 遇到的问题和解决方案\n7. 三个方案改进建议（基于UIAutomation的能力）"}],"timestamp":1772178626011}}
